{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, a corpus needs to be represented in numbers.",
    "Various representation and feature extraction techniques are shown in Figure 11.",
    "Popular feature extraction techniques include word embedding and character embedding, POS-Tag and word2vec, n-gram, chunk, and skip-gram.Word embedding is converting words into numbers in the form of vectors or arrays [76].",
    "Word embedding ranks at the top of feature extraction techniques.",
    "It relates to the deep learning approach that NER researchers have widely used in recent years."
  ]
